---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Stefano D'Ambrosio">
  <section class="bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500/[0.03] to-cyan-500/[0.03]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-32">
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-center font-serif text-5xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-12 text-center text-foreground/70">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-foreground/80 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          This site uses <strong>Google Tag Manager</strong> to manage analytics. When you accept
          cookies, anonymized usage data (pages visited, browser type, session duration) may be
          collected via Google Analytics. No personally identifiable information is collected unless
          you voluntarily submit it through the contact form.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Contact Form</h2>
        <p>
          When you submit the contact form, we receive your name, email address, and message. This
          data is sent via email and is not stored in any database. We use it solely to respond to
          your inquiry and never share it with third parties.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Contact form submissions are retained in our email inbox until you request deletion.
          Analytics data is retained for 26 months per Google Analytics' default retention policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          <li>File a complaint with your local data protection authority</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          This site uses Google Tag Manager and Google Analytics. Google's use of this data is
          governed by their
          <a
            href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
            class="text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
          >
            Privacy Policy
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions or requests regarding your data, reach out at
          <a
            href="mailto:stedamb@protonmail.com"
            class="text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
          >
            stedamb@protonmail.com
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
